(20, 'Indian Bareacts', '<p>CourtsJudgments provides legal real time information of over 3 lakh+ bare acts and other related materials in print, electronic and web format. It is dedicated to providing reliable, secure, powerful and simple solutions to all your legal requirements. CJ offers a wide range of Legal Commentaries, Student Texts, Bare Acts, Digests, Books, Journals, eBooks, eProducts as well as publications in fields allied to law. In today&#39;s digital life, it is imperative that the information we seek is available across an array of devices that now run our lives. In order to facilitate a more convenient access to our website. It is a database of all Central enactments which are in force and their subordinate legislations made from time to time. With the help of this system, retrieving of any Central Act and its relevant subordinate legislations of one&rsquo;s interest in an up-to-date form has been simplified and made extremely user-friendly and accessible at push of few buttons. Subscription to a comprehensive range of subject-wise, country and state law reports and journals are&nbsp;also available to provide you the best of case law and statutory law. Renowned law reports offered include Supreme Court Cases, All India Reporter, Criminal Law Journal, SCC (Criminal), Business Law Reports, SCC (Labour &amp; Services), SCC (Civil), and ICLR&#39;s English Law Reports. In this section, you can access full database of all the Central BareActs passed by the Indian Parliament by searching the India Code Information System (INCODIS).State Acts are also available here.Users can access all the Rules passed by the Parliament and State Legislative Assemblies. Subordinate legislations issued by various Departments are also given in this section. The aim behind this platform is to provide a single window access to the information of all type of judgements , bareacts and documents related to law and services being provided by the Indian Government for citizens and other stakeholders. An attempt has been made through this platform to provide comprehensive, accurate, reliable and one stop source of information about India and its various facets.</p>\r\n', '', NULL, NULL, NULL);
